== Diagram Pattern ==

Each diagram uses a **wrapper + Mermaid** two-page pattern:

* **Wrapper page** (e.g. ##Governance Structure/WebHome.xwiki##) — A short page with a title and a ##{{include}}## macro that pulls in the Mermaid source. This is what users navigate to.
* **_Mermaid page** (e.g. ##Governance Structure_Mermaid/WebHome.xwiki##) — Contains only the ##{{mermaid}}## block. Kept separate so it can be ##{{include}}##d from multiple locations without duplicating the diagram source.

New diagrams should follow this pattern. Always use Mermaid syntax (not images) so diagrams remain editable and version-controlled.